gffParser
Class GFF3

java.lang.Object
  gffParser.GFF3
Direct Known Subclasses:
CDS, Exon, Gene, MRNA, StartCodon, StopCodon
public class GFF3
extends Object

Each GFF3 object is a row in the GFF3 file. A GFF3 Object can be decorated, as see in CDS, Gene, Exon, StartCodon, and StopCodon

Author:
Vincent Xue
